messages.message: <!here> I'm working on the new text editor and I'd love some more templates to add to it for UDFs. If you have any you want to add please create a new page like this one: https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/PEXP/pages/143229001/Refiner+Function+Basic. If you could include a title, description, and code snippet.

Two ideas that come to mind:
1. UDFs that access the filesystem (a la https://dogfood.instabase.com/docs/reference/apps/flow/udfs-in-flow/)
2. UDFs that do logging (also documented here https://dogfood.instabase.com/docs/reference/apps/flow/udfs-in-flow/)
Btw I have to say I am _beyond_ excited for the text editor changes!
